	<h1 class="title">戴森家又出了一个做灯的，和吸尘器一样高级</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/system/users/faces/49398/small/49398.jgp?1422272111" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">Josh Rubin</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-06-22 08:28:00 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/10973/medium/10973.jpg?1436644052" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


